content.rendered:
Directed By Vishesh Agrawal. Danish Ansari. Vikram Arora. Alia Bhatt. Gauri Khan. Imtiyaz Khan. Dharam Soni. Gaurav Verma

Written By Parveez Sheikh . Jasmeet K Reen. Vijay Maurya. Jasmeet K Reen. Parveez Sheikh

Stars Alia Bhatt (Badrunissa Sheikh). Shefali Shah (Shamshunissa). Vijay Varma (Hamza Sheikh). Roshan Mathew (Zulfi). Rajesh Sharma (Qasim). Vijay Maurya (Police Inspector Raja Ram Tawde). Santosh Juvekar (Police Officer Jadhav). Kiran Karmarkar (Damle). Puja Sarup (Beautician (as Pooja Swaroop)). Inayah Chowdhry (Childhood Badru (as Inayah Chowdhary)). Vikram Pratap (Abdul (as Vikram) )

Language Hindi

Producers Vishesh Agrawal. Danish Ansari. Vikram Arora. Alia Bhatt. Gauri Khan. Imtiyaz Khan. Dharam Soni. Gaurav Verma

Production Eternal Sunshine Productions. Red Chillies Entertainment
